, surreal battlefield experience\n- Sniping, shoot at the longest 4Km VR sniper range ever", "short_description": "The most Realistic, Physics Based, Gun Simulator. Grab your gun with physical hands, and shoot bullets that are physically calibrated to real life. \n\nKEY FEATURES\n- Realism, everything feels just like real life, and guns have real world weight, and recoil\n- Gun Variety, over 100+ guns, scopes, attachments, and counting\n- Enemies, realistic enemies to shoot and fight\n- Wargame, fight over 20 AI in one map, surreal battlefield experience\n- Sniping, shoot at the longest 4Km VR sniper range ever"}]}, "developer_name": "Alto Interactive", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://github.com/superdude12399/PrivacyPolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Alto Interactive", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://discord.gg/zdX9PCt", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3744040075834813"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "484106329729341"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "586021627164092"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "918770903145051"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "337024725105993"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "918770903145051"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1734807600, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "586021627164092"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_suppo